%% Software Factory Operating States - What to Expect

stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> NoSprint: no open sprint issue

  NoSprint --> AutopilotHousekeeping: autopilot starts
  SprintReady --> AutopilotHousekeeping: autopilot starts

  AutopilotHousekeeping --> NoSprintEvaluated: housekeeping completes, no open sprint
  AutopilotHousekeeping --> SprintEvaluated: housekeeping completes, open sprint remains

  NoSprintEvaluated --> FactoryCycleQueued: autopilot dispatches factory cycle
  FactoryCycleQueued --> FactoryPlanning: target workflow is not busy
  FactoryCycleQueued --> NoSprint: target workflow already busy or dry run

  FactoryPlanning --> NoSprint: preflight finds an existing sprint and short-circuits
  FactoryPlanning --> SprintReady: ideation, research, strategy, and sprint planning complete

  SprintEvaluated --> TrackerLoopQueued: autopilot dispatches tracker loop
  TrackerLoopQueued --> SprintExecuting: target workflow is not busy
  TrackerLoopQueued --> SprintReady: target workflow already busy or dry run

  SprintExecuting --> PRReview: child issues produce agent/issue-* PRs
  PRReview --> ReviewFixes: code review requests changes
  ReviewFixes --> PRReview: fix-pr updates PRs
  PRReview --> AutoMergeQueue: PRs approved and ordered by tracker
  AutoMergeQueue --> SprintExecuting: more unchecked tracker children remain
  AutoMergeQueue --> SprintComplete: tracker children are done

  SprintComplete --> NoSprint: housekeeping closes completed sprint tracker

  state "Manual control-plane follow-up" as ManualControl
  FactoryPlanning --> ManualControl: proposed .github/workflows/** change
  SprintReady --> ManualControl: tracker item requires .github/** change
  SprintExecuting --> ManualControl: issue branch detects .github/** requirement
  ManualControl --> NoSprint: human resolves or re-scopes work
